For the swapping of diagonals of 2 triangles with
a common edge to increase the quality, it is necessary
that the triangles are in a same plane, or in planes
with normal vectors with a small angle.

ANGL2P is this angle, in degrees, under of it the 2
triangles are supposed co-planar.

A reasonabily value is under 10 degrees.
If more, the geometry can be strongly modified!
